#. translators: the placeholders are opening and closing tags for bold
#: admin/options.php:111
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Both modes run without any external paid service. %1$sSelf-hosted%2$s "
"generates challenges via the WordPress REST API. %3$sCustom%4$s lets you "
"point to your own ALTCHA-compatible backend."
msgstr ""
"どちらのモードも外部の有料サービスなしで動作します。%1$sSelf-hosted%2$s は "
"WordPress REST API を介してチャレンジを生成します。%3$sCustom%4$s を使用する"
"と、独自の ALTCHA 対応バックエンドに接続できます。"

#. translators: the placeholders are opening and closing tags for bold
#: admin/options.php:130
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The Spam Filter acts on the classification returned by a %1$sCustom%2$s "
"backend. It has no effect in %3$sSelf-hosted%4$s mode, which uses proof-of-"
"work only."
msgstr ""
"Spam Filter は %1$sCustom%2$s バックエンドから返される分類に基づいて動作しま"
"す。PoW (proof-of-work) のみを​​使用する %3$sSelf-hosted%4$s モードには影響しま"
"せん。"

